title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Midday' game
title_page: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Midday' game
maintext:
COLUMBIA, S.C. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday afternoon’s drawing of the South Carolina Lottery’s “Pick 4 Midday” game were:
9-4-0-2
(nine, four, zero, two)
